fields.name: timestamp
fields.doc: Time of the measurement, floored to 15 sec

fields.name: xname
fields.doc: Unique identifier for the CDU of the measurement, e.g. x2007c1. The CDU xname is the xname of the neighboring cabinet

fields.name: col
fields.doc: Col index of the cdu. (Note this the col of the neighboring cabinet.)

fields.name: power
fields.doc: AC Input power to the CDU (unit: W, interval: 15 sec)

fields.name: liquid_inlet_0_flow_primary
fields.doc: Liquid Inlet 0 Liquid Flow Primary, i.e. the facility supply flowrate (unit: gal/min, interval: 1 min)

fields.name: liquid_inlet_0_temperature_primary
fields.doc: Liquid Inlet 0 Temperature Primary i.e. the facility supply temperature (unit: degC, interval: 1 min)

fields.name: liquid_outlet_0_temperature_primary
fields.doc: Liquid Outlet 0 Temperature Primary i.e. the facility return temperature (unit: degC, interval: 1 min)

fields.name: liquid_inlet_0_pressure_primary
fields.doc: Liquid Inlet_0 Pressure Primary i.e. the facility supply pressure (unit: lbs/in^2, interval: 1 min)

fields.name: liquid_outlet_0_pressure_primary
fields.doc: Liquid Outlet 0 Pressure Primary i.e. the facility return pressure (unit: lbs/in^2, interval: 1 min)

fields.name: liquid_outlet_0_flow_secondary
fields.doc: Liquid Outlet 0 Liquid Flow Secondary i.e. the rack supply flowrate (unit: gal/min, interval: 1 min)

fields.name: liquid_inlet_1_temperature_secondary
fields.doc: Liquid Inlet 1 Temperature Secondary i.e. rack return temperature (unit: degC, interval: 1 min)

fields.name: liquid_outlet_1_temperature_secondary
fields.doc: Liquid Outlet 1 Temperature Secondary i.e. the rack supply temperature (unit: degC, interval: 1 min)

fields.name: liquid_inlet_1_pressure_secondary
fields.doc: Liquid Inlet 1 Pressure Secondary i.e. the rack return pressure (unit: lbs/in^2, interval: 1 min)

fields.name: liquid_outlet_1_pressure_secondary
fields.doc: Liquid Outlet 1 Pressure Secondary i.e. the rack supply pressure (unit: lbs/in^2, interval: 1 min)

fields.name: pump_1_input_pressure_secondary
fields.doc: Pump 1 Input Pressure (unit: lbs/in^2, interval: 1 min)
